    SOA Exam PA - R Package Documentation

    This project is to generate a website hosting R package documentations for the SOA Exam PA: Predictive Analytics.

    • Please visit the GitHub Page for documentations
    • Please consider starring this repo if you find it helpful
    • Please raise an issue if you have any suggestions, comments, and concerns

    Development Logs

    This repo contains an R package named PAdocs which finds the appropriate versions of the R packages given date of syllabus update

    > get_pkg_version()

29:      xgboost 0.90.0.2 2019-08-01

    We fetch the packages from the CRAN mirror on GitHub and then build documentations using pkgdown.

    The meta data for the PAdocs package is set in the R/PAdocs.R file.
